										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><a href="https://www.ruleranalytics.com/blog/inbound-marketing/lead-generation-statistics/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">The vast majority</a> of marketers say generating leads is their number one priority. Know what that means? There are a bunch of smart people out there fighting to attract the leads you need to convert.</p>
<p>We&#8217;ll need to think big to win that race, so we asked some of our favorite marketers for the boldest, best-performing lead generation ideas they‚Äôve created or seen in the wild.</p>
<p>They delivered. These lead-gen examples bring in a ton of business because they‚Äôre crazy creative and perfectly tuned to their target audiences. Swipe them to inspire your next campaign.</p>
